  <brief_title>NAVASET: Nava Level Titration Using Comfort Scales</brief_title>
  <official_title>Neurally Adjusted Ventilatory Assist (NAVA) Levels Titration During Weaning Using Ventilatory Comfort Scales: a Physiological Evaluation</official_title>
